item.title: SoftLayer_Container_Account_Internal_Ibm_Request
item.description: SoftLayer_Container_Account_Internal_Ibm_Request Datatype Description Contains data required to both request a new IaaS account for active IBM employees and review pending requests. Fields used exclusively in the review process are scrubbed of user input. associatedMethods SoftLayer_Account_Internal_Ibm::requestAccount SoftLayer_Account_Internal_Ibm::getAccountTypes Local accountType Purpose of the internal IBM account chosen from the list of available Type: string address1 If no address information is available in BluePages, will use this Type: string
